2020-05-21
new: SERVER_getWarnWhenUpdateJobsAreDelayed: Gets the tolerable amount of running/waiting time to finish an update job.
new: SERVER_setWarnWhenUpdateJobsAreDelayed: Sets the tolerable amount of running/waiting time to finish an update job.
new: I18N_getTimeDateAndElapsedMinutes: Takes a timestamp, calculates its date and time sting in the given language and the minutes from the timestamp to the current time.
