new: Added OptionPage*.php for Ubuntu 20.04.
new: CFDiskBasic::runIfEFIPartInvalid: Takes BASH commands (for partitioning and formating) and executes them only, if EFI is not used, the commands are NOT ment for the drive the EFI partition is on or the EFI partition itself and if the EFI partition is invalid.
new: CFDiskBasic::efiCheckOnClient: Checks the validity of an EFI partition diretly on the m23 client, if EFI is used and writes the result to /tmp/efiCheck.result.
