new: CATSG::pickDesktops: Randomly picks desktops from the list of desktops that are available in the distribution.
new: CATSG::simplifyNames: Simplifies server, sourceslist and desktop names.
new: CATSG::getVMName: Generates a (unique) name for the VM.
new: CATSG::getFileName: Generic filename generator.
new: CATSG::getLogFile: Get the log filename.
new: CATSG::getBashFile: Get the name of the BASH file that contains the full test set for an m23 server.
new: CATSG::log: Logs BASH code with the resulting exit and (optionally) exits when a failure occurs.
