2018-09-22
patch 101167: Fixes for editing clients and Kerberos settings for UCS 4.2
fix: edit_client.php, client_details.php: The new clearSession variable loads the client name and ID into the session. Without it the client name and ID would be set one time only and not changed afterwards. As consequence one client could be edited only.
