new: PKG_getDuplicatedIdenticalJobs: Returns an array with a list of all jobs that are identical by package, priority, status and params.
new: PKG_removeDuplicatedIdenticalJobs: Removes all jobs that are identical by package, priority, status and params omitting the first job.
new: CLIENT_recoverClientCombineJobs: Recover a client: all client jobs are done again, status is set to 0, all identical jobs are combines.
