2015-10-28
new: UCS_udmSuccessOrErrorMessage: Takes the output from an udm command and checks for the return code (must be a single number in the last line). If the return code is non-zero, all lines above the last line are treated as error message and written to $errorMessage.
+++++
2015-10-27
new: UCS_delClient: Removes a client from the UCS LDAP.
cha: getServerNetmask: Now scans bridges on UCS too.
cha: CLIENT_deleteClient: Now calls UCS_delClient, if the m23 server runs on UCS.
cah: DHCP_activateBoot: Now can deaktivate network boot on UCS too.
new: UCS_getEtc_ucr_master: Gets the contents for /etc/univention/ucr_master on the client.
new: UCS_enableClientLDAP: Enables LDAP authentification on the client on the UCS.
