cha: CChecks::checkBootType: Added BOOTTYPE_GRUB2EFIX64.
new: CClient::getNetworkBootTypesArrayForSelection: Generates an array with all avaialable network boot types for using it in a selection.
cha: DHCP_addClient: Added support for UEFI.
cha: m23 / postinst: Now changes the ramdisk size in /m23/tftp/grub/grub.cfg too.
