new: CClient::getModifyDateHumanReadable: Returns the last modified date in human readable form.
new: CClient::getInstallDateHumanReadable: Returns the installation date in human readable form.
new: CClient::generateHTMLClientNameBar: Generates an URL with the client name linking to the client details page.
new: CClient::generateHTMLPackagesBar: Generates an URL with the amount of the client's packages linking to the client packages page.
new: CClient::generateHTMLWaitingAllJobsBar: Generates an URL with the amount of the client's waiting jobs and all jobs linking to the change jobs page.
