new: m23SHARED_DBname: Generates a database name for m23 shared by input and salt.
new: m23SHARED_getDBnameByInterface: Calculates the database name for m23 shared by setting in the user interface
new: m23SHARED_getDBnameByClient: Gets the database name for m23 shared as part of the client ID.
new: m23SHARED_init: Checks if a m23shared environment is present, sets the variables in the session and chooses the according DB.
new: m23SHARED_new: Adds a new m23shared user and creates a new DB.
new: m23SHARED_setLicense: Sets the maximum allowed amount of clients and the evaluation time in days.
new: m23SHARED_evaluationDaysLeft: Calculates how many days are left from evaluation period.
