cha: m23normalInstall.php: Now reports dependend packages that got installed automatically and sets these install jobs to done.
new: MSR_markm23normalAsDone: Marks comming m23normal install jobs as done if the packages they would install are already installed. This may happen when a package with dependencies is installed.
new: PKG_fastGetInstalledPackages: Gets a list of all installed packages (faster than dpkg --get-selections).
new: PKG_fastGetNewInstalledPackages: Gets new installed packages by comparing status files (before and after the installation).
