cha: PKG_downloadPool, POOL_createExtendedPackageIndex, POOL_makeRepository: Now uses SERVER_runInBackground instead of directly calling screen.
fix: m23image: Removed proxy settings from apt.conf.
fix: m23/postinst: Creates MySQL m23dbroot user with less privileges because ALL PRIVILEGES is not possible.
