new: client_details.php: Added icon for CUPS. Now can access the CUPS server of the m23 clients.
new: m23PrinterConfigInstall: Configures CUPS for administration thru the m23 server and allows all clients in the network to print on the remote printer.
fix: PKG_addPackageSelection: Now adds only valid packages.
fix: EDIT_commentout: Now works if only the match parameter is given.
fix: m23PrinterConfigInstall: Now installs the printer packages one by one to make sure that the most possible amount is installed.
