2006-08-24
new: RAID_create: Creates a RAID of different drives or partitions.
new: LVM_init: Scans for existing volume groups and activated all found volumes.
new: LVM_createVolumeGroup: Creates a volume group. With multiple calls you can join multiple devices or partitions to.
new: LVM_createLogicalVolume: Creates a logical volume. This logical volume can be used like a normal partition.
