cha: khtml2png: has been mostly rewritten, because KDE 3.2 now uses an optimisation that doesn't draw widgets that aren't visible. With the old tool it is impossible to make screenshots bigger than the screen. The new tool scrolls the contents of the HTML page and makes different screenshots that are appended to one image.
