2019-09-15
cha: PKG_preparePackageDir: Now has a detection for possible PrivateTmp systemd redirection of /tmp'
new: SERVER_waitForLock: Cyclically and randomly waits until a lock file isn't existing and creates it at once.
cha: SERVER_runInBackground: Now has extra parameter to use SERVER_waitForLock instead of the locking inside the BASH script.
