2015-03-11
cha: CFDiskIO::isFreeSpaceBetween, CFDiskIO::getCreatablePartitionTypes, CFDiskIO::isNewPartitionOfTypeCreatable: Added support for EFI partitions.
cha: CFDiskIO::virtualAddPartition: Added check for disallowing EFI partitions on BIOS systems and vice versa.
new: CClient::getInstPargetEFIPartDevtDev: Gets the EFI partition of the client.
new: CClient::setEFIPartDev: Sets the EFI partition of the client.
cha: CFDiskBasic::makeInstPartBootable: Becomes CFDiskBasic::makeInstOrEFIPartBootable and has support for EFI partitions now.
new: CFDiskBasic::EFItypeAndGUIDJob: Sets EFI boot partition type and GUID for the EFI boot partition and adds it to the list of partition steps.
cha: downloadExtractRFS: Added gdisk.
cha: CFDiskBasic::genPartedCommands: Now Sets EFI boot partition type and GUID for the EFI boot partition too.
