new: CPool::setPoolRelease:Sets the release value of the pool.
new: CPool::getPoolType: Gets the type value of the pool.
new: CPool::setPoolArch: Sets the type value of the pool.
new: CPool::getPoolArch: Gets the architecture value of the pool.
new: CPool::setPoolArch: Sets the architecture value of the pool.
new: CPool::setProperty: Writes the contents of a property file
new: CPool::getProperty: Reads the contents of a property file
new: CPool::getSize: Calculates the disk usage of a pool.
new: CPool::setPoolDir: Sets the name of the pool and makes sure, the pool directory exists.
new: CPool::destroyPool: Deletes the pool
