2009-03-17
new: CLIENT_getClientID: Returnes the ID of the calling client.
new: VM_statusIcons: Returns HTML codes that include the VM status icons of the client.
cha: CLIENT_generateHTMLStatusBar: Now uses VM_statusIcons.
new: VM_setVisualPassword: Sets the password for the login to the visual management console on the host for all guests.
new: VM_setVisualURL: Sets the URL to connect to the visual management console.
cha: vnc4server-m23-vbox: Added parameter for the IP of the m23 server.
