cha: Changed size of field "cpu" in the table "clients" to 255 to allow informations about multiple CPUs.
cha: getHardwareData: Now stores names and speeds of all CPUs.
cha: m23hwscanner: Found Linux systems are now written only with the device name only to lilo.conf. (e.g. sdb1 instead of /dev/sdb1)
cha: CIR_detectSCSI: Added ata_piix to modules list.
+++++
