2019-06-04
patch 101268: Compatibility fixes for Debian 8.
new: autoTestScriptGenerator.php: Generates test sequences for m23-autoTest for m23 servers with Debian 8 + 9 (32 and 64 bits), UCS 4.3 + 4.4., Raspbian, localhost and m23 server installation ISO.
fix: m23 / control: Now depends strongly on php-bz2, but does'n require it, if PHP 5 is used. This makes it compatible with Debian 8 (again).
fix: m23 / postinst: Configuring Squid is compatible with Debian 8 (again).
