new: CFDiskBasic::createUEFIPartition: Creates a new UEFI partition with a size of 512 MB at the start of the disk (if possible).
new: CFDiskIO::virtualAddDisk: Adds a new virtual disk.
new: CFDiskIO::createRaidDisk: Creates a new RAID disk.
