new: clientLiveLogComplete.php: Shows the complete live log of a client.
new: CLIENT_touchLiveLogFile: Touches the live log file of a given client and returns the full name of the log file (with directory).
fix: CLCFG_genFstab: "--force" parameter for grub is not valid any more.
