fix: CLCFG_genFstab: Fix for the LiLo filter.
patch: Changes to support LiLo better.
cha: CLCFG_genFstab: Now filters out double entries in lilo.conf. This may happen on RAID systems and hinder lilo to install.
cha: installLilo: Links update-grub to lilo now.
