2008-08-04
cha: checkdisklabel: Now only executes mklabel if parted doesn't return warnings. This suppresses a parted stack smashing error.
cha: m23hwscanner: Changed the code to remove some compiler warnings.
cha: CLCFG_genFstab: Added extra checks for Ubuntu Hardy/Intrepid to install GRUB correcty.
cha: CLCFG_genFstab: Extra checking for m23hwscanner, because m23hwscanner-ubuntu can not be installed on newer Ubuntu version. Instead the normal m23hwscanner is needed and installed here.
