new: menuVarDel: removes a global variable from /tmp/menuVars.
new: createRFSFinishInitrd: Umounts the initrd image, configures the kernel file and compresses initrd. These steps are needed to build the bootimages.
new: createRFSImage: Creates an empty image file for the root filesystem
new: createRFSCopyKernelNModules: copies the kernel and modules to the root filesystem
