new: GRP_exists: checks, if a group exists
new: GRP_add: adds a group
cha: create_group.php: uses group functions
new: GRP_getIdByName: gets the Id of a groupname
new: GRP_del: deletes all clients from the group and the group itself
cha: removed "groupname" from table "clients"
new: CLIENT_getId: returnes the id of a client
new: GRP_isClientInGroup: returnes true, if a client is in the selected group, otherwise false
new: GRP_addClientToGroup: adds a client to a group
new: GRP_delClientToGroup: removes a client from a group
