dbimg.tgz		- added ntpdate + execute @ startup
			- added hdparm + dma autodetection @ startup
			- added libmysqlclient
m23remasterImg.sh	- fixed: /oldroot and / aren't tared 
log2db			- introducing tool, saves logfiles to db
			
+++++
