patch 101082: Release 18.1
release 18.1
cha: ubuntu/DISTR_afterChrootInstall: Now moves wgetrc out of the way before installing wget and move wgetrc back afterwards. Needed sometimes (!) when m23 server is and UCS and client distribution Linux Mint 18.3 32bits.
