2017-10-18
new: SERVER_setServerBoolSetting: Sets a bool value of a server setting.
new: SERVER_getServerBoolSetting: Gets the boolean value of a server setting.
new: SERVER_isLiveLogDisabled: Determines, if live logging should be disabled globally for all clients.
new: SERVER_setLiveLogDisabled: Sets/Unsets live disabling of logging globally for all clients.
new: SERVER_isUpdatePackageInfosDisabled: Determines, if the updatePackageInfos job should NOT be added to any clients.
new: SERVER_setUpdatePackageInfosDisabled: Sets/Unsets the updatePackageInfos job should NOT be added to any clients.
new: SERVER_isClientOnlineStatusEnabled: Determines, if the online status of all clients should be detected and shown.
new: SERVER_setClientOnlineStatusEnabled: Sets/Unsets if the online status of all clients should be detected and shown.
