2016-06-09
new: MAIL_gpgCheckKey: Checks, if a GPG key ID has a valid private or public key.
new: CGPGSign::checkKey: Checks, if the GPG is valid as public and private key.
new: MAIL_gpgGettKey: Gets the public GPG key as ASCII.
new: CGPGSign::exportPublicSignKey: Exports the public key to the webserver directory.
