cha: CPoolFromClientGUI::__construct: Now doesn't download the base packages.
+++++
2013-04-13
new: HELPER_xargsRecursive: Executes a BASH command with a list of arguments. If the BASH command fails, the argument list is split in two parts and recursively executed again.
+++++
2013-04-07
cha: CPoolFromClientGUI::__construct: Now creates a package selection too.
new: CPoolFromClientGUI::saveInObjectStorage: Saves this object in the object storage.
new: CPoolFromClientGUI:: showCheckboxForAddingm23BuildPoolFromClientPackage: Shows a checkbox, that adds a m23BuildPoolFromClient job when checked.
cha: client_distr.php: Now calls CPoolFromClientGUI:: showCheckboxForAddingm23BuildPoolFromClientPackage.
