2009-12-08
new: SERVERBACKUP_showConfigurationDialog: Shows a dialog for configuring the server backup.
new: MAIL_importGPGKey: Imports an GPG key into the bunch of GPG keys.
new: MAIL_deleteGPGKey: Deletes an GPG key from the bunch of GPG keys.
