cha: IMG_showCreateImage: Creation of an imaging is now done from a network booted client.
new: CLIENT_resetAndInstall: Resets or wakes the client to boot from network and run jobs.
+++++
2008-03-12
new: CLCFG_dialogGaugeProcPos: Generates the BASH code for showing a dialog with status bar that uses /proc/pid/fdinfo for current file position.
new: IMG_getExtractedSize: Gets the size of the extracted image by its name.
cha: IMG_clientRestore: Now uses CLCFG_dialogGaugeProcPos to show a nice status bar on writing the image.
