2006-09-02
cha: FDISK_getDrivesAndPartitions, FDISK_listDrivesAndPartitions: New parameter pathFilter: Set this to another value than false if you want only devices with a given string in it. If you add an "!" the beginning all is given out that doesn't contains the filter string (without the "!").
fix: FDISK_dev2LDevLPart: Now can search for partition number 2 (and higher).
new: FDISK_addDrivePartitionToRaid: Adds a drive or partition to a RAID.
