2004-10-13
cha: CLCFG_installBasePackages: now sets do_boot_enable to "No" in kernel-img.conf. there are new questions while installing the kernel, that don't allow automatic installation of the kernel if do_boot_enable is set to "Yes". Lilo is run afterwards, so there is no problem booting the client.
