cha: FDISK_getFreeSpaceBeforeFristPartition, FDISK_getBeforeFristPartitionPercent, FDISK_getFreeSpaceAfterLastPartition, FDISK_getAfterLastPartitionPercent: are now removed, because they were used at one place only and were wrapper functions for FDISK_getAfterLastPartition or FDISK_getBeforeFristPartition. The main functions are used directly now.
