cha: MSG_showInfo, MSG_showError, MSG_showWarning: Now uses MSG_show.
fix: FDISK_addDrivePartitionToRaid, FDISK_addFstab, FDISK_addPart, FDISK_addRaidBeforeFormat, FDISK_autoPart, FDISK_delFstab, FDISK_delPart, FDISK_dev2LDevLPart, FDISK_formatExisting, FDISK_formatPart, FDISK_fstabAddDialog, HTML_listSelection, HTML_storableCheckBox, HTML_storableInput, HTML_storableSelection, IMG_getFormatCompressionFromFile, MAIL_attach, PKG_listRecommendSubPackages, POOL_getCDDistributionRelease: Corrected deprecated call-time pass-by-reference.
