new: SERVER_addAdmin: Adds an administrator with all access rights.
new: SERVER_delAdmin: Deletes an administrator with all access rights.
new: SERVER_getM23RemoteAdministrationServiceMsg: Gets the account data block from pasted message.
new: SERVER_getM23RemoteAdministrationServiceRandomKey: Generates a random key (once) for the m23 remote administration service and returns it on every call.
new: HELPER_generateSalt: Generates a random salt string.
