2010-09-15
fix: FDISK_fdiskSessionReset: Now resets the session values correctly.
cha: CIR_enableDropbear: Now sets the network boot password only, if the / is mounted with rootfs (that indicates that Linux is run from the RAM disk).
release m23 rock 10.4
fix: getPartType, getPartFS: Now supports RAIDs that don't have a partition type.
fix: PKG_hasOptions: Now detects correctly, if an option page exists.
