new: CLIENT_setDebconfDB: Sets debconf values for a client and a package.
new: CLIENT_runDebconf: Generates BASH code to import debconf settings from the DB into the debconf of the client.
cha: m23normalInstall.php: Now runs CLIENT_runDebconf.
cha: m23normalInstall.php: Changed DB query result to associative array.
