cha: HTML_selection, HTML_checkBox: Added support for saving the value to the session.
new: HTML_storableCheckBox: Shows a check box with label with loading and storing the checking state to and from the session.
new: HTML_storableSelection: Shows a list of radio buttons or a selection with loading and storing the checking state to and from the session.
