patch: New experimental functions for combining LDAP and home on NFS with mass installation.
new: LDAP_getNextID: Returns the next higher than the highest ID
new: LDAP_getNextUserID: Returns the next higher than the highest user ID
new: LDAP_addNewID: Adds a new ID to the table of used IDs or returns "false" if the ID exists
new: LDAP_deleteID: Delets an ID from the table of used IDs
new: LDAP_addNewUserID: Adds a new user ID to the table
new: LDAP_addNewGroupID: Adds a new user ID to the table
new: LDAP_getNextGroupID: Returns the next higher than the highest group ID
cha: LDAP_addPosix: now uses LDAP_addNewUserID and LDAP_addNewGroupID
cha: CLIENT_showAddDialog: now uses LDAP_getNextGroupID and LDAP_getNextUserID
