cha: sources.list: commented out non-us servers from server's sources.list
new: getRamDiskSize: gets the ramdisk size of the kernel from the kernel config file
cha: mkBootImage.sh, mkRescue.sh: now uses getRamDiskSize to create a ramdisk image of the correct size
new: mkBootImage.sh: writes kernelRamDisk.inc that contains a variable that helds the kernel ramdisk size
cha: DHCP_writePXEcfg: now uses kernelRamDisk.inc
cha: menuClientISO, menuBootCD: now writes kernel variables every time
new: bootimage: now contains SATA modules and SCSI emulation
