cha: hwdetect.php: adjusted pathes to the files
cha: plugin.php: exchanged all error and info messages with the versions from message.php
new: /m23/bin/pscheck: script to check if a process is running
fix: /m23/bin/phpDebug, /m23/bin/phpNormal: checks if apache is running. if not start it
